{"title":"安卓邮件客户端设置","icon":"android","shareable":true,"id":"guide/account/mail/android","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"text","type":"tip","text":["本教程将指导您如何在安卓（Android）设备上配置学校邮箱。","教程以 Gmail 客户端为例，其他客户端的设置流程类似。"]},{"tag":"ul","text":["打开邮件客户端，选择“添加其他账号”。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-1.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"ul","text":["在账号类型中选择“其他”。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-2.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"ul","text":["输入您的学校邮箱地址（例如 `username@nenu.edu.cn`）。","点击左下角的“手动设置”。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-3.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"ul","text":["账户类型选择“个人(IMAP)”。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-4.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"ul","text":["输入您的邮箱密码。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-5.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"ul","text":["将“接收服务器”地址设置为："]},{"tag":"action","content":"imaphz.qiye.163.com"},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-6.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"ul","text":["将“外发服务器”地址设置为："]},{"tag":"action","content":"smtphz.qiye.163.com"},{"tag":"text","type":"warning","header":"关于服务器地址的说明","text":["尽管学校官方提供了「smtp.nenu.edu.cn」作为服务器地址，但由于其尚未配置有效的安全证书，可能导致多数邮件客户端无法添加该邮箱，或在使用中频繁弹出安全警告。","在学校解决此问题前，建议您统一使用网易官方提供的服务器地址。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-7.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"ul","text":["根据个人需求，选择合适的同步频率。"]},{"tag":"text","type":"note","text":["请注意，同步频率越高，手机的电量消耗也可能相应增加。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-8.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"ul","text":["最后，设置您希望显示的帐户名称与发件人姓名。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail/gmail-9.jpg","watermark":true}],"time":"2025 年 7 月 23 日 09:43:28"}